  "detailed_description": "<br>Find latest news, teasers, suggestions/feedback, FAQ on our official discord!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/3feb9c6658ecdfd3d1f6b3f416d237d1.avif?t=1752271453\" width=600 height=69 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/2174b181e2639d1042d45547eb9078a2.poster.avif?t=1752271453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/2174b181e2639d1042d45547eb9078a2.webm?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/2174b181e2639d1042d45547eb9078a2.mp4?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enjoy online co-op with up to 4 players!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/00540dffb3428758f98394bd0526d031.webp?t=1752271453\" width=600 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/ea45fc76473d4e5cb362e8a48df7d74f.poster.avif?t=1752271453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/ea45fc76473d4e5cb362e8a48df7d74f.webm?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/ea45fc76473d4e5cb362e8a48df7d74f.mp4?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/308bc09acd762a5078dddf2c503644d3.poster.avif?t=1752271453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/308bc09acd762a5078dddf2c503644d3.webm?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/308bc09acd762a5078dddf2c503644d3.mp4?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fight, level up, buy, survive! Choose from multiple stages! Can you do it? Start off at level 1 with only your character's unique weapon. As you fight mobs, they will drop XP, which you can collect to level up. Leveling up opens up a shop where you can purchase new equips or upgrade your current ones in order to become stronger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/29daeed01a6f003763d8e5638d6e8e8a.webp?t=1752271453\" width=600 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/c770090040e5a70b53c4f88017c2619d.poster.avif?t=1752271453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/c770090040e5a70b53c4f88017c2619d.webm?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/c770090040e5a70b53c4f88017c2619d.mp4?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/53a6603758f0358a125c5624a982c27a.poster.avif?t=1752271453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/53a6603758f0358a125c5624a982c27a.webm?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/53a6603758f0358a125c5624a982c27a.mp4?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fight 50+ unique bosses! Explore the catalogue of items! As you play, bosses will appear, each with their own unique attacks and abilities. Each stage has their own set of bosses. The more you play, the more you will become familiar with the available items, increasing your odds of success.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/ed503237b3066ab54b3365769fdd4f43.webp?t=1752271453\" width=600 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/5c18c7765bcd377c979ad18dc7b563c2.poster.avif?t=1752271453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/5c18c7765bcd377c979ad18dc7b563c2.webm?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099220/extras/5c18c7765bcd377c979ad18dc7b563c2.mp4?t=1752271453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Currently, there are 30+ playable characters. As the game is still in Early Access, we have plans to continually add more and more playable characters, each with their own unique set of skills and playstyles for you to try.",
